'''甲基橙'''是一种常用的[[酸碱指示剂|酸碱指示剂]]，因为它在不同pH值下的颜色变化清晰明显：在25摄氏度时，甲基橙在pH小于3.1的介质中呈红色，在pH大于4.4的介质中呈黄色。因此它通常用于酸的滴定。

==指示剂颜色==
[[File:Methyl_orange_02035.JPG|200px]]
在酸度降低的溶液中，甲基橙从红色变为橙色，最后变为黄色，而酸度增加的溶液中则相反。
{{pH_indicator_template|indicator_name=甲基橙|low_pH=3.1|high_pH=4.4|low_pH_color=red|low_pH_text=white|high_pH_color=yellow}}
甲基橙在{{convert|25|C}}的水中的pK<sub>a</sub>为3.47。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1021/j100670a024 | title = Kinetics of acid dissociation-ion recombination of aqueous methyl orange | year = 1972 | last1 = Sandberg | first1 = Richard G. | last2 = Henderson | first2 = Gary H. | last3 = White | first3 = Robert D. | last4 = Eyring | first4 = Edward M. | journal = The Journal of Physical Chemistry | volume = 76 | issue = 26 | pages = 4023–4025}}</ref>

==其他指示剂==
{{Main|pH指示剂}}
{{pH_indicator_template|indicator_name=甲基橙-二甲苯蓝|low_pH=3.2|high_pH=4.2|low_pH_color=#884488|low_pH_text=white|high_pH_color=#00CD00}}
由甲基橙和[[二甲苯蓝|二甲苯蓝]]的溶液组成的指示剂，随着溶液碱性增强，颜色从灰紫色变为绿色。

==安全==
甲基橙有[[突变|突变]]性。<ref name=sciencelab>[https://www.sciencelab.com/msds.php?msdsId=9926081 MSDS] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512223610/https://www.sciencelab.com/msds.php?msdsId=9926081 |date=2014-05-12 }} from ScienceLab.com, Inc. Retrieved 2011-09-24</ref>

